{
  "texts": [
    "Color bars denote raw counts.",
    "The SpatialData framework comprises a core package, spatial data and associated satellite packages napari-spatialdata, spatialdata-io and spatialdata-plot, compatible with Python 3.9 and above.",
    "All code is available on GitHub as part of the scverse organization and is licensed under the permissive 'BSD 3-Clause License'.",
    "The project structures inherit from the scverse cookiecutter and the napari plugin cookiecutter, thus implementing unit tests and precommit checks in a continuous integration setting.",
    "The documentation is built using Sphinx and hosted on Read the Docs."
  ]
}